Package: TauStar
Type: Package
Title: Efficient computation of the t* statistic corresponding of Bergsma and Dassios (2015)
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-9-30
Author: Luca Weihs
Maintainer: Luca Weihs <lucaw@uw.edu>
Description: Computes the t* statistic corresponding to the tau star population coefficient introduced by Bergsma and Dassios (Bernoulli 20(2), 2014, 1006-1028) and does so in  O(n^2*log(n)) time. Can provide both the V-statistic and U-statistic related to the tau star measure depending on user preference.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.4)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Suggests: testthat
